interpretations.definition:
means any process for—
(i) making an article;
(ii)assembling or joining any article whether by chemical process or otherwise;
(iii) adapting for sale any article;
(iv)packaging, bottling, putting into boxes, cutting into pieces, cleaning, polishing, wrapping, labeling, or in any other way whatsoever preparing for sale any article otherwise than in a retail stores for the purpose of sale in such store exclusively and directly to the consumer;
